#

Kung Pao Chicken with Cashews

25 min
$12.5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

SoyNuts

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinNut-Free Option Available

Cuisine:

ChineseAsian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

Quick MealStir-FryAsian Cuisine

Description

A quick and flavorful stir-fry dish featuring tender chicken, crunchy cashews, and spicy peppers, all tossed in a savory sauce.

Ingredients

  • boneless chicken breast: 1 pound
  • cashews: 1/2 cup
  • bell pepper (red or green): 1
  • green onions: 1/2 cup
  • soy sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • rice vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (minced): 1 teaspoon
  • sesame oil: 1 tablespoon
  • dried red chilis: 2-3
  • cooked rice: to serve
